# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  ProValley Site Intelligence — Environment Variables
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  Copy this file to .env and fill in your values.
#  .env is gitignored and should NEVER be committed.
#
#  In Vercel: add these under Project → Settings → Environment Variables
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# PageSpeed Insights API Key (free, unlimited quota for reasonable use)
# 1. Go to https://console.developers.google.com
# 2. Create a project (or use an existing one)
# 3. Enable the "PageSpeed Insights API"
# 4. Create an API key under Credentials
# VITE_ prefix exposes the variable to the React client bundle.
VITE_PSI_KEY=your_psi_api_key_here
